    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Capital Float Ventures Solutions. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Software Engineer to strengthen our Srinagar-based team.\n\nAbout Capital Float Ventures Solutions:\nCapital Float Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Capital Float Ventures Solutions!",
